item.title: Honourable mention "International Photographer of the Year 2015"
item.description:
Honourable mention "International Photographer of the Year 2015"

Very happy to have received an honourable mention from IPOTY - International Photographer of the Year for my work on the Sperm Whale standings for the Photojournalism category selected from more than 3,000 entries:http://iphotographeroftheyear.

item.title: Nominee "Fine Art Photography Awards 2015"
item.description:
Nominee "Fine Art Photography Awards 2015"

Fine Art Photography Awards (FAPA) London, UK (30 July, 2015) announces winners of 1st FAPA competition. Photographer José Javier Delgado Esteban was nominated in Nature for the entry entitled (untitled) at 1st Fine Art Photography Awards competition. In 2015 Fine Art Photography Awards received more then 3000 submissions from 77 countries around the world.

item.title: THIRD PLACE WINNER - Nature: Wildlife (AMATEUR) - José Javier Delgado Esteban (Spain)
item.description:
THIRD PLACE WINNER - Nature: Wildlife (AMATEUR) - José Javier Delgado Esteban (Spain)

IPOTY prestigious photography competition will help you obtain greater exposure, achieve international recognition and win some great prizes. Be recognized and rewarded for your photographic accomplishments, submit your best work to the International Photographer of the Year

item.title: Bronze Medal "PX3 Prix de la Photographie Paris 2015"
item.description:
Bronze Medal "PX3 Prix de la Photographie Paris 2015"

José Javier Delgado Esteban of Spain was Awarded: Third Prize in category Nature for the entry entitled, " Whale Nation: "Humpback Whales of the South Pacific" . The jury selected PX3 2015's winners from thousands of photography entries from over 85 countries.

item.title: Winner "Fine Art Photography Awards 2015"
item.description:
Winner "Fine Art Photography Awards 2015"

Fine Art Photography Awards (FAPA) London, UK (30 July, 2015) announces winners of 1st FAPA competition. Photographer José Javier Delgado Esteban was awarded First Prize in Wildlife / Animals for the entry entitled Whale Nation: Humpback Whales of the South Pacific at 1st Fine Art Photography Awards competition.

item.title: Bronze Medal "International Photographer of the Year Award 2016"
item.description:
Bronze Medal "International Photographer of the Year Award 2016"

Very happy to have received a Bronze Medal (Third place winner) on the Nature category from IPOTY - International Photographer of the Year for our work with Humpback Whales of the South Pacific selected from more than 3,000 entries...
